1000 solved samurai sudokus
  by printable-sudoku-puzzles.com
-------------------------------------------------------_
Each line contains 81x5=405 numbers (one solved samurai sudoku)
Each set of 81 numbers corresponds to one 9x9 sudoku within the samurai sudoku
    Positions 0-81: is the result of the top left 9x9 sudoku
    Positions 82-162: is the result of the top right 9x9 sudoku
    Positions 163-243: is the result of 9x9 sudoku in the center
    Positions 244-324: is the result of the bottom left 9x9 sudoku
    Positions 325-405: is the result of the bottom right 9x9 sudoku
